City of Bergen, Norway, is issuing an 80mln Canadian dlr eurobond, due April 13, 1994, priced at101-1/2 with an 8-5/8 pct coupon, lead manager Bank of TokyoInternational Ltd said.    The issue will be sold in denominations of 5,000 dlrs andlisted in Luxembourg. Fees are 1-1/4 pct for selling and 5/8pct for management and underwriting combined. Payment date isApril 13, 1987. There will be two co-lead managers. REUTER&#3;